nodes.text: Zobyteeg was a male individual who served as a General Council Assistant in Lutris on the Expansion Region world of Tynna. Shortly before the Clone Wars, Zobyteeg was working at the Tynna Central Government Building when it was destroyed by stone mites. The first to alert local security, he was later interviewed about the event by HoloNet News, telling the interviewer that he realized something was wrong when he was afforded a clear view of Lutris Lake despite the fact that his office did not possess a window.
Zobyteeg first appeared in HoloNet News Vol. 531 #53, an article on the HoloNet News website in 2002.
